        						        						<h1 class="artist"><a href="artist/Elton-John/4617">Elton John</a></h1>
        					</div>
        					<p class="artist hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg"><a href="artist/Elton-John/4617">Elton John</a></p>
        												<p class="artist-bio">Sir Elton Hercules John, CBE (born Reginald Kenneth Dwight on 25 March 1947) is an English rock singer-songwriter, composer, pianist and occasional actor. He has worked with lyricist Bernie Taupin as his songwriter partner since 1967; they have collaborated on more than 30 albums to date.</p>
							<p class="artist-bio-link">
